[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man in court over T in the Park campsite assault video

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has appeared in court charged with assault at the T in the Park campsite at Strathallan Castle.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Marius Bauba was arrested after a video which appeared to show a man being hit with a bottle circulated online.
The 22-year-old, of Ayr, made no plea or declaration to a single charge of assault to injury during a private hearing at Perth Sheriff Court.
The case was continued until next week for further examination and Mr Bauba was remanded in custody.
